                               <handNote>Black letters against ochre background. The inscription is written entirely in majuscule. Superscripts letters. Omega with crosslet. In line 6 tau with a star. Mu with its middle bar forms a tau. Double point after συνδρομῆς, Ἰω(άννου), Γερακ[ιώτη] Μουτου]λλά, αὐτοῦ. Use of diaeresis over iota in Ïρίνης (l. 6), Ïουλίω (l. 7). Middle dot after μηνί, εἰς. Horizontal wavy line above the abbreviation of  Ἰω(άννου). Letters ΠΤ, HΝ, ΟΥ in ligatures. Sporadic use of accents and breathings. Text between two ruled white coloured lines. Letter height: <height unit="cm">5,5-7,5</height>
